).
</paragraph>
<caption doi="10.3897/zookeys.893.39032.figures12-16" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/361388" pageId="0" pageNumber="135" start="Figures 12–16" startId="F2">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="135">
